<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">The function of the</b> <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">IOBOARD_DRAWER PBA 1</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr ">12PBA10 </compcodenr></comp> </title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="GUID-34C6A3E5-E809-4139-80CC-275A8CCF9EDC"><p class="- topic/p ">What is the function of the <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">IOBOARD_DRAWER PBA 1</compname><compcodenr class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr " translate="no">12PBA10 </compcodenr></comp>? 
</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Functional description</category></metadata></prolog><conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody "><section id="GUID-F5034822-753A-4C8B-A7CD-E44CE7EBD702" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Functional description</title><p class="- topic/p ">The IOBOARD_DRAWER PBA is a power driver board which controls the sensor/actuators for the following functions: 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Media loading 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> External output (except EXO_WIND_CLAMP_MO, EXO_WIND_FLAP_MO, EXO_WIND_DRV_MO) 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Optional: Jumbo roll interface 
</p></li></ul><p class="- topic/p "> Two remote bus interfaces are implemented, X84 upstream connected to Umorpf, X83 downstream currently not used. 
</p><note id="GUID-5C5D9BC7-31C7-468F-A77A-91AE352E1EF0" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">The 2 connectors (RJ45) are identical. Please note the correct position. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> The board has dedicated power supply inputs for the various functions. These can be continuous available or interlocked (controlled by DISTRIBUTION). 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-3FB66718-8ED1-44BE-A121-BA8FEB120620" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="GUID-B74D1C58-4633-4BDE-8EA9-982AAF9DFE67" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-42E4C700-30A7-4AEB-AACD-57AEF340569D-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-42E4C700-30A7-4AEB-AACD-57AEF340569D-svg.svg"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> 
